title: Pandelela - the famous Malaysian diver in isolation
description:
Imagine not spending one birthday with your family for over a decade. This was the price of success for Malaysian diver Pandelela Rinong Pamg. Her life on the road has left her lonely. The two-time Olympic medallist has been on coronavirus lockdown with her brother - catching up on some overdue family time.

For more episodes, videos, and more: https://www.olympicchannel.com/podcast/
